==name glinfo

==short-description

Display information about the currently installed graphics libraries.

==argument enum library

The library of interest.

==enum-value egl

Embedded-system Graphics Library.

==enum-value openvg

Open Vector Graphics Library.

==enum-value opengles

OpenGLES Library.

==enum-value memory

Print any memory usage information about the graphics libraries. Currently displays the GPU memory info from the eglQueryProfilingDataNOK EGL extension.

